Package org.aavso.tools.vstar.data

Interface Summary
IOrderedObservationSource Classes implementing this interface are a source of ordered, valid observations.
 

Class Summary
CommentCodes This class stores the possible array of comment codes
DateInfo This class store Julian Day and corresponding calendar date information.
InvalidObservation This class corresponds to a single invalid variable star observation.
Magnitude This class represents a magValue including uncertainty and fainter-than information.
Observation The base class for all file-sourced observation classes.
ValidObservation This class corresponds to a single valid variable star observation.
 

Enum Summary
CommentType This enum represents "comment code" found in all data sources.
MagnitudeModifier This enumeration represents a magnitude modifier type.
MTypeType This type enumerates valid mtype (magnitude type) values.

ValidationType This enum represents "validation flag" found in all data sources.
